I'd highly recommend having a trip sitter, they should be someone you really trust and are comfortable being yourself around. Having a good trip sitter can be a life saver. It also depends on the setting whether that be in your room at night or outside on a nice warm day. If you're feeling like its a bad idea then don't take anything, but dont get that confused with feeling a little nervous because thats normal. Its important to try your best to stay calm and if you feel like doing something will help your trip go smoother than do it. For example one time when the shrooms started kicking in I felt like this one certain black and white blanket was radiating bad energy and was giving me negative vibes so I put it somewhere I couldn't see and my trip went smoothly. Ultimately its up to you and dont take anything without doing proper research and feeling prepared.
